\[\frac{\epsilon}{D}=\frac{f_{0}-f_{f a r}}{f_{f a r}}=\cdots=\frac{f_{\text {lens }} \cdot\left(z_{\text {far }}-z_{0}\right)}{z_{\text {far }} \cdot\left(z_{0}-f_{\text {lens }}\right)}\]

